-- Monte Paschi Sees Potential to Expand in Italy, Viola Tells Sole
-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 2012-04-01T10:52:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/monte-paschi-sees-potential-to-expand-in-italy-viola-tells-sole.html
Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA 
has room to open more branches in  Italy , General Manager
Fabrizio Viola told daily  Il Sole 24 Ore  in an interview.  The company also plans to gradually reduce its financial
portfolio by at least 10 billion euros ($13 billion), Viola
added, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Vasarri in Rome at 
